  <TITLE>Limitation on adding JS/CSS resources to the bundle</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>nopCommerce version: 4.50 At the moment, we have limitation on adding the following resources: 1. Resources that output to HTML by a condition (e.g. Razor `@if()`). We've submitted a [pull request](https://github.com/ligershark/WebOptimizer/pull/209) to the WebOptimizer repository with a fix and are waiting for the approval. 1. Resources that are registered before other resources they are using (e.g. some .js file using JQuery library cannot be registered before jQuery). We can't specify weight or sort files because WebOptimizer doesn't have API for it.</DESCRIPTION>
